T1  - Partially anticipated events: A model of stock price reactions with an application to corporate acquisitions
AU  - Malatesta, Paul H.
AU  - Thompson, Rex
JO  - Journal of Financial Economics
VL  - 14
IS  - 2
SP  - 237
